                <note rend="inline" type="source">823.00/287: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">McMillin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-05T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 5, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Strictly confidential. In your opinion is will of majority of people of Peru
                    expressed in support of action of Leguia in overthrowing Pardo and calling for
                    new elections. Give Department available figures for Leguia and figures for
                    Government candidate in recent election.</p>
                <p>Have you discovered any tangible proofs of plot to defraud Leguia. Cable
                    reply.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
